snippet.title: MapleStory 2 Official Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
MapleStory 2!  Play Free Now on PC at http://www.playmaple2.com 
Dream. Create. Discover. MapleStory 2 10/10 Official Global Launch!  

Get ready to explore limitless creative possibilities as we celebrate MapleStory 2’s highly anticipated official global release!  

Take a stroll down Maple Street with us, and see just how much better everything can be MapleStory 2.  Customize your epic hero, build your dream world, and get ready to explore a whole new dimension of the MapleStory universe in this brand new worldwide phenomenon: your only limit is your imagination.  Adventurers welcome!  

Play for free at http://www.playmaple2.com
